You do not lose faction for killing bears anywhere except Surefall Glade.  The bears there are protected by the druids of the glade and they would be rather upset if you walked out of the cave with a bear pelt across your back.  Otherwise they are fair game.  Grizzley pelts and High Quality bear pelts make great money earners at low levels.  Now if I could just find a way to get one of those cool bear hats from Halas...
