About the druids teleportation.<BR>The 'ring' that druids teleport to are druid rings, that resemble the Stonehenge, which was supposed to be a place of sacrafice and druidic magic.<P>The Rings in the game are like the ruins of the Combine Empire, or better known as wizzy spires, these are string in ancient magic and thus wizzards can teleport to them. The druid rings are the same for druids, being strong in magic that allows them to teleport to each one.<P>Rigess Phillbin<BR>30 Druid<BR>Order of Vallon<BR>Vallon Zek.<P>--------------------<P>Shogu<P>'The sign of a great man is not his deeds done, but the deeds he plans to do.'<BR>'Trespassers will be violated. Survivors will be shot.' - Darksinger, who borrowed it from a horror movie.
